## Why VERITAS Matters

Traditional compliance is slow, expensive, ambiguous, and inconsistent across jurisdictions.  
Web3 has the opposite problem: fast but unverifiable.

VERITAS resolves this contradiction by delivering:

- On-chain enforcement  
- Real-time validation  
- Deterministic auditing  
- Cross-jurisdiction alignment  
- A shared truth model for enterprises, regulators, and protocols  

This is the first infrastructure to merge the speed of Solana with enterprise-grade compliance in a legally interoperable framework.

---

## Token Framework (Non-Speculative Utility)

The VERITAS token (VRS) is strictly a functional unit of computation.  
It:

- Attests transactions  
- Enforces compliance execution  
- Powers jurisdiction checks  
- Collateralizes rule verification  
- Applies slashing for invalid attestations  
- Aligns operators toward accurate reporting  

There is no yield, no reward pool, no promise of return, and no value representation.  
Its purpose is verification, not speculation.

